#component-buttons
  h4 Buttons

  br

  .row 
    .col.md-5
      p.lead.
        Buttons can be created with <code>seed-css</code> by simply adding the class <code >.btn</code> 
        to any <code >&lt;a/&gt;</code> or  <code >&lt;button/&gt;</code> element. Adding the class 
        <code >.btn-primary</code> it will become a primary button. 
 
    .col.md-5.md-offset-1.align-center
      a.btn(href="#!") a.btn
      
      br.hide-on-medium-and-up

      button.btn(type="button") button.btn
      
      br.hide-on-medium-and-up

      input.btn(type="button", value="input.btn")

